		<td><b>NES CPU/PPU in a playchoice 10</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />this may be a weird question to some, but i was wondering if it were possible to stick a nes cpu and ppu into a playchoice 10. i have someone who wants me to rgb mod their nes and i was wondering if i could the playchoice 10 up and running afterwards using the bits i strip out.
<br />
<br />thanks in advance <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

